00:17:03,800 --> 00:17:08,179
Sepertinya perjalanan Xue Rucheng ke Barat Daya diganggu oleh Leng Peishan.

259
00:17:08,179 --> 00:17:09,739
Dia selangkah lebih maju.

260
00:17:09,740 --> 00:17:12,140
Yah, Tuan Muda Jing dan mereka...

261
00:17:13,430 --> 00:17:16,139
Pangeran Komando An tidak pernah bertindak semberono.

262
00:17:16,139 --> 00:17:20,389
Kalau dia berani ke sana bersama Jing Yi dan orang-orangnya,

263
00:17:20,389 --> 00:17:21,860
